Class Administrator

java.lang.Object
entity.EntityObject
entity.user.User
entity.user.HospitalStaff
entity.user.Administrator
public class Administrator extends HospitalStaff
The Administrator class represents a specific type of hospital staff who has administrative privileges. It extends the HospitalStaff class and inherits its properties and methods, while specifying the role as ADMINISTRATOR.
